content: The gross profit margin of 48.8% improved by 490 basis points compared to the prior year period of 43.9%, driven by our growing share of CPM revenues and a higher share of countries with prepaid duties charged to the customer as for example, in the U.S. During the third quarter, marketing expenses increased to EUR23.3 million compared to EUR22.1 million in the prior year quarter, primarily due to the increase in number of our customers acquired.
